data.title: Iziaslav Dmitri Yaroslavich Rurikids, Grand Prince of Kiev (1024
data.meta_description: Iziaslav Dmitri Yaroslavich Rurikids, Grand Prince of Kiev was born in the year 1024 in Kievan Rus, within present Ukraine, son of Yaroslav "The Wise" Grand Prince of Kiev and Ingegerd (Estrid,Astrid,Alvhild) Olofsdotter of Sweden, Swedish princess and a Grand Princess of Kiev., they gave birth to 1 child. He died on October  3, 1078. This information is part of Family tree Cromer/Russell/Buck/Pratt by Elizabeth Cromer on Genealogy Online.
